Body: I want an Iot Agents that support Interaction models: Active Attributes. My choice is OMA LWM2M, I am wondering whether there is another choice is same or better?
OMA LWM2M is also supported by the OneM2M standard so it is a good option. However, a simpler one might be the UL2.0 over HTTP or MQTT.
Thank you for your helpful answer.
